C_agar_par_total.message: Total tangential drag coefficient for agar in kg/s

C_agar_perp_total.message: Total rod normal drag coefficient in agar in kg/s

C_water_par_total.message: Total rod tangential drag coefficient for water in kg/s

C_water_perp_total.message: Total rod normal drag coefficient for water in kg/s

Medium.message: Normalized medium drag coefficient (0 = water, 1 = agar)

N_segments.message: Number of body segments on each side, dorsal and ventral

R_min.message: Minor radius of prolate ellipse body in m

beta_D.message: Diagonal passive damping constant in s

beta_L.message: Lateral passive damping constant in s

beta_M0.message: Baseline active damping constant in s

kappa_M0.message: Baseline active muscle spring constant in kg/s

NSEGS.message: Number of segments in the body

NSEGSSR.message: Number of segments sensed by each stretch receptor

NSR.message: Number of stretch receptor in DA, DB, VA and VB, equal to number of units

NmusclePerNU.message: All the way down to 24, in groups of 3 per unit
